ThinkPart(
    type='think',
    think='Now I have a clear picture. The tests in `matching_bloc_test.dart` al
ready expect the fly-out to happen after `SwipeAnimationCompleted` emits `_lastL
istState` and then `SwipeActionSubmitted` performs the fly-out. But wait, the cu
rrent tests expect:\n\nFor `SwipeDragEnded` with threshold exceeded:\n1. `Matchi
ngLoadSuccess` with offset\n2. `MatchingLoadSuccess` with reset offset (from `_o
nSwipeAnimationCompleted`)\n3. `MatchingSwipeInProgress` with fly-out (from `Swi
peActionSubmitted`)\n4. `MatchingLoadEmpty`\n\nFor `SwipeAnimationCompleted` dir
ect:\n1. `MatchingLoadSuccess`\n2. `MatchingSwipeInProgress` with fly-out\n3. `M
